org.knime.core.node.workflow

Class NodeGraphAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.workflow.NodeGraphAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<NodeGraphAnnotation>

    public final class NodeGraphAnnotation
extends Object
implements Comparable<NodeGraphAnnotation>
    Wrapper holding graph annotation information for a node in a workflow such as position in nested scopes, layered depth etc. to make subsequent graphs operations more efficient.
    Since:
    2.8
    Author:
    M. Berthold
